// ================================================
// ALL STATUS EFFECTS
// ================================================

**Substitute** 🪵  
**Start of turn effect**: None  
**Active effect**: None  
**Triggered effect**: Absorbs incoming damage (reduces its own duration). Removed when duration reaches 0.  
**End of turn effect**: None  

**Sling** ☄️  
**Start of turn effect**: None  
**Active effect**: Fires a Barrage at the target.  
**Triggered effect**: None  
**End of turn effect**: None  

**Shadow Clone** 👥  
**Start of turn effect**: None  
**Active effect**: Each clone performs Barrage on the target.  
**Triggered effect**: Absorbs damage (reduces clone duration). Removed when duration reaches 0.  
**End of turn effect**: None  

**Water Clone** 👥  
**Start of turn effect**: None  
**Active effect**: Each clone performs Barrage on the target, then applies Wet (or +2 duration) to the target.  
**Triggered effect**: When blocking an attack, splashes the attacker with Wet (3 turns or +2 duration). Removed when duration reaches 0.  
**End of turn effect**: None  

**Doom** 💀  
**Start of turn effect**: Deals set damage (usually 1) to the character.  
**Active effect**: None  
**Triggered effect**: None  
**End of turn effect**: None  

**Regen** 🌿  
**Start of turn effect**: Heals set amount (usually 1) if below max HP.  
**Active effect**: None  
**Triggered effect**: None  
**End of turn effect**: None  

**Dome** 🪨  
**Start of turn effect**: None  
**Active effect**: None  
**Triggered effect**: Blocks non-Genjutsu attacks. Reduces duration by 1 each block. Removed when duration reaches 0.  
**End of turn effect**: None  

**Wildfire** 🕯  
**Start of turn effect**: None  
**Active effect**: Deals 1 damage to target + applies Burn to both target and self.  
**Triggered effect**: When owner is attacked, applies Burn to the attacker.  
**End of turn effect**: None  

**Burn** 🔥  
**Start of turn effect**: Deals set damage (usually 1) to the character.  
**Active effect**: None  
**Triggered effect**: None  
**End of turn effect**: None (can be removed by Wet interaction)  

**Wet** 💦  
**Start of turn effect**: None  
**Active effect**: None  
**Triggered effect**: None  
**End of turn effect**: If the character also has Burn, removes Burn completely and reduces Wet duration by 1.  

**Numb** ⚡️  
**Start of turn effect**: Skips the character's turn and removes itself.  
**Active effect**: None  
**Triggered effect**: None  
**End of turn effect**: None  

**Charged** 🔋  
**Start of turn effect**: None  
**Active effect**: None  
**Triggered effect**: None  
**End of turn effect**: None  
(Used by Chain Lightning to increase number of hits on repeated casts)  

**READY** 💪  
**Start of turn effect**: None  
**Active effect**: Breaks opponent's triggered defenses, then performs Barrage.  
**Triggered effect**: None  
**End of turn effect**: None  

**Release** 🌀  
**Start of turn effect**: None  
**Active effect**: None  
**Triggered effect**: When hit by Genjutsu, removes the effect and ends turn early.  
**End of turn effect**: None  

**Bleed** 🩸  
**Start of turn effect**: Deals set damage (usually 1) to the character.  
**Active effect**: None  
**Triggered effect**: None  
**End of turn effect**: None  

**Recovered** 💫  
**Start of turn effect**: None  
**Active effect**: None  
**Triggered effect**: None  
**End of turn effect**: If the character also has Numb, removes both Numb and Recovered.  

**Dog** 🐺  
**Start of turn effect**: None  
**Active effect**: Each Dog performs Bite (1 damage + Bleed to target, heals itself +1 duration).  
**Triggered effect**: Absorbs damage equal to its duration. Removed when duration reaches 0.  
**End of turn effect**: None